name: ReindeerNames
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: reindeer names
des:
Have some Christmas fun by learning how to recite the names of Santa's reindeer.

There are two modes:
Practice mode : Alexa will read out the reindeer names and you have to say the name for each reindeer (remember the order as you will need to get them in order for the challenge mode)

Challenge mode: Alexa will start off by asking you to say "Dasher" then she'll ask you 'Which reindeer comes after Dasher?' You have to say the next reindeer in the same order as practice mode. 

The order of the reindeer is: Dasher, Dancer, Prancer, Vixen, Comet, Cupid, Donner, Blitzen and Rudolph

Rudolph has been included as recent stories have depicted Rudolph at the front of the pack.

Privacy Information
This skill does not collect or store any personal information. Data collected by the skill is not shared with any third party and is only used for the purpose maintaining the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
